    <para id="import-auto-id1165067802859">Under reverse bias, Zener Breakdown immediately occurs as the Emax at the mettalurgical junction exceeds the critical field as shown in Table 3.3.2. Hence total I-V characteristic is as shown in Figure 3.22.G.</para>
    <figure id="import-auto-id1165077767242">
