    <para id="import-auto-id1595659">As seen in Figure 3.22.G. there are two features of Tunnel Diode:</para>
    <list id="import-auto-id1165077697451" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-roman">
      <item>It is highly non-linear ;</item>
      <item>And it has a strong N-Type Negative-Impedance Region(NIR) characteristics.</item>
    </list>
    <para id="import-auto-id1165066876059">The I-V characteristics of Tunnel Diode is parameterized as shown in Figure 3.23.</para>
    <figure id="import-auto-id1165057147907">
      <media id="import-auto-id1165058072823" alt="">
        <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/Picture 8-f809.png" height="367" width="442"/>
      </media>
    </figure>
